Product Brief
Goal
Build a web-based study platform where college students can create profiles, share academic content, collaborate in study groups, receive AI-powered learning assistance, and connect with peers through messaging.

Features
User Authentication â€” Secure registration and login system allowing students to create accounts and access the platform.

Profile Management â€” Students can create and edit profiles containing academic information (major, year, courses, interests) and professional details (skills, projects, experience).

Post Creation and Feed â€” Users can create, publish, and view posts containing academic insights, project updates, questions, and study resources with text and media support.

Study Group Discovery â€” Browse and search available study groups filtered by subject, course, or interest area.

Study Group Creation and Management â€” Users can create new study groups, set group details (name, description, subject area), and manage group membership.

Group Collaboration Space â€” Within each group, members can share resources, discuss topics, and coordinate study sessions through a dedicated group feed and discussion area.

AI Learning Assistant â€” Provide personalized study recommendations, content suggestions based on user's academic profile and activity, and answers to academic questions.

Direct Messaging â€” One-on-one chat functionality enabling students to message peers and mentors privately.

Data Persistence â€” Use the platform-hosted persistent database to store user profiles, posts, groups, messages, and all application data.

